My heart breaks for all of the war and division in this world. This is one of my favourite songs in the world and playing it feels more important than ever. God Unites and is inside ALL OF US, regardless of background, ethnicity, religion, belief, we are all one family, all made in the eyes of the same God, all expressions of the same godliness. May we all treat each other and each living being as HOLY. May war and division end. 
Lokah Samastah Sukhino Bhavantu, In sha’ Allah, Amen, In Lak’ech Ala K’in, Peace may be
